  <p>â€¢ Oblate rotational ellipsoid: x2/a2 + y2/a2 + z2/c2 = 1 (a2 &gt; c2)<br />
â€¢ Prolate rotational ellipsoid: x2/a2 + y2/a2 + z2/c2 = 1 (a2 &lt; c2)<br />
â€¢ Two-sheet rotational hyperboloid: x2/a2 + y2/a2 â€“ z2/c2 = â€“1<br />
â€¢ One-sheet rotational hyperboloid: x2/a2 + y2/a2 â€“ z2/c2 = +1<br />
â€¢ Rotational paraboloid: z = aÂ·(x2 + y2)
